	(182,12,'跑酷最初由法国消防员发起，2002年在英国开始盛行，后来大卫贝利（]DavidBelle）把它发扬光大。法国电影[Banlieue 13]（暴力街区）即是展示PARKOUR街头文化，主角DAVID BELLE是LE PARKOUR运动的','跑酷,的,来源,跑酷,最初,由,法国,消防员,发起,','跑酷最初由法国消防员发起，2002年在英国开始盛行，后来大卫贝利（]DavidBelle）把它发扬光大。法国电影[Banlieue 13]（暴力街区）即是展示PARKOUR街头文化，主角DAVID BELLE是LE PARKOUR运动的','<div class=\"nw_cot\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		&ldquo;跑酷&rdquo;最初由法国消防员发起，2002年在英国开始盛行，后来大卫&middot;贝利（]DavidBelle）把它发扬光大。法国电影[Banlieue 13]（暴力街区）即是展示PARKOUR街头文化，主角DAVID BELLE是LE PARKOUR运动的创始人之一。</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		　</p>\r\n	<div class=\"img img_c pr\" style=\"WIDTH: 600px\">\r\n		<a href=\"http://a3.att.hudong.com/43/53/19300001350915132962537490342.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"跑酷\"><img alt=\"跑酷\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/150604/0100255200-0.jpg\" title=\"跑酷\" /></a><strong>跑酷</strong></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		　 在Parkour的世界里, 练习者称谓&ldquo;Traceur&rdquo;。Parkour 的动作是结合了所有自由的动作, 提升创意，并且鼓励人们去找到属于自己的信仰。在Parkour的领域里，不少Traceur极力想表现flips、spin这些未收录的的动作, 这也表达出了Parkour并不局限于某些固定的动作，甚至你也能够把自己的&ldquo;独门武功&rdquo;加到Parkour里面。Parkour的动作追求的是出其不意 的效果，往往超出了常人的想象。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-09-01 18:21:02'),
	(183,13,'跑酷 骨折是指由于外力的作用，破坏了骨的完整性和连接性。骨折分为闭合性骨折和开发性骨折。 骨折的象征： (1)疼痛。 (2)肿胀和皮下淤血。 (3)功能障碍。 (4)骨折部位畸形、异常活','跑酷,骨折,了,怎么办,跑酷,骨折,是指,由于,','跑酷 骨折是指由于外力的作用，破坏了骨的完整性和连接性。骨折分为闭合性骨折和开发性骨折。 骨折的象征： (1)疼痛。 (2)肿胀和皮下淤血。 (3)功能障碍。 (4)骨折部位畸形、异常活','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;骨折是指由于外力的作用，破坏了骨的完整性和连接性。骨折分为闭合性骨折和开发性骨折。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">骨折的象征：</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(1)疼痛。（有较明显的肢体异位）</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(2)肿胀和皮下淤血。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(3)功能障碍。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(4)骨折部位畸形、异常活动和伴有骨擦声，有压痛和震痛感。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(5)可用X光检查证实。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">处理方法如下：</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(1)止痛抗休克。（冷敷，但要防止冻伤）</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(2)伤口处理。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(3)固定制动。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(4)及时、安全护送到医院接受治疗。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151121/1-151121221336463.png\" style=\"width: 193px; height: 182px;\" /></div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(184,14,'The way is the path of silence.Cut across town quietly at your own speed. 跑酷 Concentrate on footwork, Your Touch, Your own sensibility. Look for cat-like silence and you will find the path... This is the way 《This is The way 》--Seba','跑酷,的,哲学,意义,The,way,the,path,si','The way is the path of silence.Cut across town quietly at your own speed. 跑酷 Concentrate on footwork, Your Touch, Your own sensibility. Look for cat-like silence and you will find the path... This is the way 《This is The way 》--Seba','<div class=\"nw_cot\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The way is the path of silence.Cut across town quietly at your own speed.</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;跑酷跑酷</strong></span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Concentrate on footwork, Your Touch, Your own sensibility.</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Look for cat-like silence and you will find the path...</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">This is the way&quot;</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">《This is The way 》--Sebastien Foucan</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">生活就像是有障碍和挑战所组成的.要克服这个过程.</span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">如果你