	(196,26,'                 ','加入,北京市跑酷委员会,申报,流程,','                 ','<div style=\"text-align: right\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;入会须知 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">一、入会条件</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、拥护本协会的章程；</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、有加入本</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">的意愿；</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、会员应遵守</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">章程，履行会员义务，执行</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">决定。严守</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">纪律，维护</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">的声誉和利益。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、会员入会审查时，如发现严重违规记录者不得加入</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">协会</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">；</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5、会员应自律并遵守国家有关法律法规，如被发现严重违规行为者将被取消会员资格。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">二、申请入会程序</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、个人会员请下载相应附件：《个人会员意向书》（请务必将会员意向书中的各项内容填写完整）。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、<span style=\"text-align: right;\">俱乐部会员（团体）会员</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: right;\">请下载《俱乐部（团体）会员意向书》，俱乐部会员费用或团体会员费用在提交意向书并通过审核后另行通知。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、企业会员等单位会员，请下载《单位会员意向书》，单位会员费用在提交意向书并通过审核后另行通知。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、意向书须填写完整后，请以清晰彩色扫描件形式提交到协会邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><strong>bjesa_freedom@163.com</strong></span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">，另将70元工本费（个人会员费用）打入北京市极限运动协会银行账户：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11050172500009005381</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;开户银行：中国建设银行北京通州潞河支行</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;备注：为了保障您的权益，请打款后务必将打款人姓名、身份证号号码通过邮箱或电话方式告知，以便确认信息无误。</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><font size=\"3\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></font><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4、通过审核后以邮件、电话形式回复，以确认申请是否通过（如审核未通过，工</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">本费将返还至您的账户）。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5、申请通过后7-10个工作日，以快递形式发放会员证。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">三、联系方法及其他</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;有意加入协会的单位或个人请先详细浏览协会网站，充分了解协会章程。为了更好的服务会员，提高协会工作效率与质量。企业有意申请者请先申请注册个人会员。企业的个人会员需由企业成员提交经审核后由其所在企业协同管理，离职者请企业成员与协会办公室联系安排除名。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">　　电话：010-80877453、18611090051</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;邮箱（ E-mail）：</span></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 16px;\">bjesa_freedom@163.com</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">　　邮寄地址：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; text-align: right; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">北京市丰台区，华星擘达商业文化园内（地铁十号线，纪家庙站</span><span style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; text-align: right; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">口，西南侧即是），b区</span><span style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; text-align: right; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">号楼</span><span style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">218</span><span style=\"font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; text-align: right; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">室。</span><span style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;收件人：北京市极限运动协会</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"http://www.parkourcom.com/uploads/soft/160923/1_1410182911.doc\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">点击此处下载 《个人会员意向书》</span></a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.bjesa.cn/uploads/soft/161215/1_2025571931.docx\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">点击此处下载《俱乐部（团体）会员意向书》</span></span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.bjesa.cn/uploads/soft/161018/1_2016589451.doc\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">点击此处下载《单位会员意向书》</span></span></span></a></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"http://www.bjesa.cn/a/huiyuanzhuanqu/ruhuiliucheng/2016/1019/39.html\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">点击此处查看《北京市极限运动协会会费管理办法》</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
