	(200,31,'行云流水 跑酷之美 上下齐心 意在全民 第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛圆满落幕 由北京极限梦跑酷俱乐部承办，北京市跑酷委员会监审的第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛于5月3日圆满落幕。来自国内','第三届,欢乐谷,跑酷,争霸赛,圆满,落幕','行云流水 跑酷之美 上下齐心 意在全民 第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛圆满落幕 由北京极限梦跑酷俱乐部承办，北京市跑酷委员会监审的第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛于5月3日圆满落幕。来自国内','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">行云流水 跑酷之美 &nbsp; 上下齐心 意在全民</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color:#b22222;\">第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛圆满落幕</span></span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 由北京极限梦跑酷俱乐部承办，<strong>北京市跑酷委员</strong>会监审的第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛于5月3日圆满落幕。来自国内外的198名参赛选手，20个跑酷团队，展开为期三天的激烈角逐。比赛过程中，选手们无不使出各自绝招，灵活穿梭在障碍物间，矫健的身手以及充满想象力的画面引得现场观众阵阵欢呼，可谓异常精彩！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151205/1-15120520215K40.png\" style=\"width: 707px; height: 333px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	参赛者合影</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;大赛组委会会很荣幸的邀请到<strong>文化部文化艺术发展中心文化创意产业研究院蔡诗章院长</strong>莅临指导工作，蔡院长在观看比赛之余也对跑酷争霸赛的竞赛方式和选手的精神面貌给予了相当的肯定与赞扬，并且对跑酷运动的未来寄予殷切期望！北京市跑酷委员会会长王伟，<strong>中国跑酷标杆人物张磊</strong>，<strong>北京市跑酷委员会秘书长、国际ITF（中国）跆拳道联盟副秘书长安利会，资深跑酷推广人刘垒占以及欢乐谷相关领导</strong>出席比赛现场，与所有参赛人员见证此次跑酷争霸赛冠、亚、季军的诞生，并为优胜者颁奖。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151205/1-151205202212M7.png\" style=\"width: 683px; height: 435px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	比赛 精彩瞬间</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第三届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛本着&ldquo;公平、公正、公开&rdquo;的原则。以&ldquo;成果展示、技术交流&rdquo;为宗旨。 大赛包含预选赛、晋级赛、决赛三个阶段。共诞生男子竞速、女子竞速、团体竞速、男子竞技、女子竞技等17个奖项。赛场竞争激烈，可谓百家争鸣，百花齐放。 本次大赛中，年龄最大的选手宋东南已年过四十，但他用他稳健的定点、流畅的穿越，证明了跑酷这项运动是不受年龄限制的。而他慷慨激昂的宣言更是将赛场的气氛推向另一个高潮：&ldquo;是跑酷让我年轻，是跑酷告诉我，遇到困难要拼一把。&rdquo;他在向障碍发出挑战，他在为他所钟爱的运动呐喊。赛场需要这样的选手，跑酷需要这样的队员！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151205/1-151205202231346.png\" style=\"width: 609px; height: 398px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	70后参赛者</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;不同年龄段的练习者对跑酷的理解不同，跑酷又给不同年龄段的练习者带来不同的收获。 青年人享受行云流水、随心所欲的跑酷动作带来的洒脱。中年人受用跑酷习练中屡败屡战历练出的的那份坚韧。预计在不久的将来老年人也能在跑酷练习中找回年轻的心态，收获健康的体魄。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151205/1-151205202301324.png\" style=\"width: 571px; height: 344px;\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;跑酷运动自2007年于中国兴起，在跑酷运动早期的发展过程中，部分发烧友的不当举动在一些媒体的大肆渲染下给跑酷带来了许多负面影响。使老百姓认为该项运动是极度危险、去平民化的。 其实不然，北京市跑酷委员会在经过详细调查与讨论之后，将跑酷分为三类：</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>第一类</strong> 极限跑酷 &nbsp;这一类的受众基础是较为窄小的，练习者在没有任何安全保护的情况下，挑战高难度的障碍。 较为危险，建议普通民众切勿轻易尝试。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>第二类</strong> 竞赛跑酷 &nbsp;这一类习练者在有安全保护的场馆内训练，提高技能，在专业人员设计的赛道上进行成果展示。比如：历届欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛就属于该类。安全可以得到保障，通过勤加练习，多数人都可以参与。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>第三类</strong> 大众跑酷 &nbsp;所谓大众跑酷就是将跑酷运动中安全、有效、适合各类身体条件的跑酷动作摘选出来，结合体适能形成的一套训练体系！人人可以习练，目的是强身健体，放松身心！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为期三天的欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛是在举办&ldquo;竞赛跑酷&rdquo;的同时，也为发展&ldquo;大众跑酷&rdquo;奠定着群众基础。大赛期间，所吸引观赛者达万人之众。赛事通过专业的解说以及引导让大家更加生动、正确、客观的了解了这一项能带给人们健康、并且没有那么危险的新兴运动。&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151205/1-1512052023521Z.png\" style=\"width: 564px; height: 462px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	北京市跑酷委员会主要成员与文化部领导合影</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;如今，在国家号召大力推广全民健身以及鼓励赛事举办的时代背景下，大赛组委会联合<strong>北京市跑酷委员会</strong>旨在将欢乐谷跑酷争霸赛发展为全国乃至全世界有影响力的赛事。通过赛事影响力的不断增加，让越来越多的潜在跑酷习练者加入到全民健身的队伍中来！为中国社会体育的发展添砖加瓦，为提高全民的身体素质贡献绵薄之力！</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/151121/1-151121215201F9.png\" style=\"text-align: right; width: 193px; height: 182px;\" /></div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(201,32,'6月5日上午，北京市极限运动协会成立大会暨第一届会员代表大会在广西大厦顺利召开。','极限,极限运动,跑酷','6月5日上午，北京市极限运动协会成立大会暨第一届会员代表大会在广西大厦顺利召开。','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK00Y18.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 367px;\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6月5日上午，北京市极限运动协会成立大会暨第一届会员代表大会在广西大厦顺利召开。来自北京市体育总会相关领导以及北京市长跑俱乐部副主席兼秘书长刘振和同志共同出席大会成立仪式并做出重要发言。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK02R05.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 367px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;会中，由来自北京市各类极限运动代表100多人，以民主投票的方式选举出会长王伟、秘书长刘垒占、副会长张磊、副会长张宁、副会长吴优良、监事长李党伟，及其他职务，并投票通过多项议程。该协会的正式成立标志着北京市极限运动行业将走入一个新的时期，对其他省、市极限运动组织发展起到重要引导作用。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK041P9.jpg\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;极限运动是20世纪末的新兴体育运动，是人类最大限度地发挥自我身心潜能，向自我身心挑战的体育项目。主要包括项目：跑酷运动、极限漂流、滑板、极限直排轮、特技单车、BMX自行车越野、速度攀岩、极限攀岩、蹦极、冲浪、极限体能等项目。而北京市极限运动协会是由各类极限运动的优秀人物自愿结成的联合性社会组织，也是目前北京唯一一家具有独立法人资格的非赢利性质的极限运动社会团体。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK055629.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 367px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会第一任会长王伟表示，协会作为连接政府与市场之间的桥梁。一定要发挥好自身的纽带作用。及时的向行业传输、普及国家的相关政策和要求，同时要将民间的诉求和呼声及时反馈于政府。为北京市争光，为中国由体育大国到体育强国的转变贡献绵薄之力。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK1112I.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 367px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;同时，北京市极限运动协会将做出行业表率，与各地区以及国际组织建立友好联系、合作，共同促进行业的良好发展，为更多爱好极限运动的人士提供一个健康有序的运动环境，以及帮助与指导。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160607/1-16060GK125138.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 266px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;最后，北京市极限运动协会将以党和国家发展体育事业的方针、政策为指导；以国家宪法，法律法规和社会主义核心价值观为准绳；致力于实现中华民族的伟大复兴的中国梦为目标，团结北京市体育工作者和极限运动爱好者，为推动该行业的发展，积极工作，指导和普及极限运动，不断提高运动技术水平，攀登高峰！</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(202,33,'6月10日端午节，由北京市极限运动协会主办的第四届全国跑酷精英赛于北京欢乐谷再燃战火，来自北京、上海、深圳、武汉等全国各地代表跑酷最顶尖水平的近百位参赛选手齐聚京城。','极限,极限运动,跑酷,欢乐谷,北京市,北京市极限运','6月10日端午节，由北京市极限运动协会主办的第四届全国跑酷精英赛于北京欢乐谷再燃战火，来自北京、上海、深圳、武汉等全国各地代表跑酷最顶尖水平的近百位参赛选手齐聚京城。','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR01AD54.jpg\" style=\"width: 548px; height: 458px;\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">　　6月10日端午节，由北京市极限运动协会主办的第四届全国跑酷精英赛于北京欢乐谷再燃战火，来自北京、上海、深圳、武汉等全国各地代表跑酷最顶尖水平的近百位参赛选手齐聚京城，共同约战极限跑酷大赛。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR04A3C2.jpg\" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; width: 1000px; height: 708px;\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此次跑酷争霸赛持续2天，由个人竞技赛、个人竞速赛环节组成。共有212人报名参加，其中跑酷界极具影响力的北京城市猴子团队、北京跑酷公社、成员多次参演动作类影视剧的河南FTF跑酷俱乐部、拥有多位外籍队员的上海LINK跑酷团队、山东SOLO、长春源动力、沈阳异行、以及把跑酷运动光大于中国屏幕的北京极限梦跑酷俱乐部等共同登场竞技。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR04613462.jpg\" style=\"width: 1000px; height: 598px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR04Q4a8.jpg\" style=\"width: 1000px; height: 734px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本次比赛首次采用积分赛制，量化评比各项比赛成绩。竞技环节第一次加入解说员形式，对选手跑酷运动进行实时解说，以帮助现场观众深入理解各种极限动作。记者在现场看到，来自全国多个地区的跑酷运动员精神饱满，身形矫健，通过攀爬、跳跃、翻腾等各种炫酷动作，灵活穿越于各式障碍物。选手们激情洋溢、活力四射，为广大北京市民奉上了一场极限刺激、动感十足的视觉盛宴。比赛休息间隙，影星甄子丹御用替身、跑酷动作指导张磊更是一身屈原装扮，为现场观众纷发粽子，为活动增添了节日的色彩。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR04520311.png\" style=\"width: 661px; height: 361px;\" /></div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;记者在现场看到，来自全国多个地区的跑酷运动员精神饱满，身形矫健，通过攀爬、跳跃、翻腾等各种炫酷动作，灵活穿越于各式障碍物。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>国家体育总局社会体育指导中心原党委书记栾开封</strong>，<strong>北京市体育总会协会部部长陈志群</strong>，<strong>北京市极限运动协会会长王伟</strong>，<strong>北京市极限运动协会秘书长刘垒占</strong>，<strong>跑酷委员会会长张磊</strong>也现身比赛现场。</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR02552393.jpg\" style=\"width: 499px; height: 329px;\" /></div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>(右1北京市极限运动协会会长王伟；左2跑酷委员会会长张磊；左3、左4北京欢乐谷副总经理)</strong></span></span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;全国跑酷争霸赛自2013年创办以来，已成功举办过4届，本次活动是目前为止国内赛程安排最全面的一次体育跑酷类活动。2016年，《全民健身计划》将进入新周期，本次举办的跑酷争霸赛正是旨在创新全民健身方式，倡导全民健身新时尚，宣传科学健身理念，充分发挥市级体育协会作用。今年的活动在保持多样性和专业性的同时，特别强调跑酷运动的群众性，向社会公众推广便于学习和锻炼的跑酷运动方式。活动期间，国内顶级跑酷高手还与市民互动，通过情景模拟实验的方式，讲解面临公众场合紧急危机时脱险的必要动作，一探求生秘技。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"http://tv.cctv.com/2016/06/11/VIDEWYoMmacG5yHU1emmi4jI160611.shtml?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0#10006-weixin-1-52626-6b3bffd01fdde4900130bc5a2751b6d1\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color:#0000cd;\">点击此处查看 CCTV5 对本次活动报道</span></span></strong></span></span></a></div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(203,34,'2016年北京市跑酷训练班火热进行中，现接收全国跑酷爱好者、跑酷零基础学员。顺利通过本次培训考核的学员，将获得由北京市极限运动协会颁发的跑酷教练执业资格证书。','跑酷,跑酷培训,跑酷训练,北京跑酷,北京跑酷培训','2016年北京市跑酷训练班火热进行中，现接收全国跑酷爱好者、跑酷零基础学员。顺利通过本次培训考核的学员，将获得由北京市极限运动协会颁发的跑酷教练执业资格证书。','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2016年北京市跑酷训练班火热进行中，现接收全国跑酷爱好者、跑酷零基础学员。顺利通过本次培训考核的学员，将获得由北京市极限运动协会颁发的跑酷教练执业资格证书，获得跑酷教练资格。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>本次跑酷训练班，分为</strong>：</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、跑酷教练执业资格认证培训班：适合有跑酷基础，有参赛需求、愿意继续进修的跑酷爱好者。）</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、跑酷零基础一级训练班：此训练班适合没有跑酷基础的跑酷爱好者，初级训练班为基础教学班，不在颁发证书一列。通过零基础培训可获得教练培训班报名资格。此训练班分为成人训练班与未成年训练班，接受不同年龄段的跑酷爱好者。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 培训导师团队</strong>：</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、全国跑酷顶尖培训导师、国内外知名跑酷运动员。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、具有多年从业经验的体适能培训导师，可帮助跑酷学员全面认识人体结构及运动知识，有效预防运动伤害，加强肌肉管理。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 报名方式：</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 热线：&nbsp;010-8087 7453（如热线咨询频繁，还可联络以下联系方式）</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 王老师：18611090051</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 王老师：15801404862（该号可加微信联络）</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">北京市极限运动协会</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2016年8月17日</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(204,35,'    ','SUP,SUP桨板公开赛,桨板','    ','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;桨板冲浪（SUP）又名直立单桨冲浪。是一项源于美国夏威夷，近年逐渐风靡全球的运动。最初，冲浪教练为了管理众多的学员，直立站在冲浪板上能获得更好的视野，便于观察周遭情况，也利于远处过来的涌浪。当时还没有专门的SUP冲浪板，用的是普通长度的冲浪板和单面的桨。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160923/2025123010-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 29px; width: 352px; height: 220px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;当代SUP运动也是同冲浪运动一样，是从夏威夷群岛开始流行起来的。20世纪60年代早期，夏威夷一队名为&ldquo;Beach Boys of Waikkiki&rdquo;（Waikiki海滩男孩）的冲浪爱好者，站在加长的冲浪板上为学习冲浪的游客们拍照，因此，&ldquo;Beach Boy Surfing&rdquo;也是SUP的另一个别称。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8月20日，由iDareX敢玩主办，北京飞人俱乐部、雷子桨板俱乐部协办的第二届北京SUP公开赛(2016)，在北京飞人基地成功落下帷幕。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160923/2024501b2-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 29px; width: 553px; height: 312px;\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为期10天的赛期，百余位玩家从全国各地赶到北京参与北京SUP桨板公开赛。比赛分为专业赛和娱乐赛，选手可以根据自己的实力，自主选择赛事。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;专业赛事分为男子男子500米、男子1000米、女子200米和女子1000米。有来自青岛、深圳、、西安、北京等各地职业选手投入比赛，让比赛更专业更具看点。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;娱乐赛也是此次SUP桨板公开赛的亮点，让业余选手可以通过游戏互动，对桨板有更多认识，从而对此次运动产生更多兴趣。落水格斗掀起了整场比赛的第一个高潮，选手分别站在两块连接在一起的桨板上，用气泡格斗棒互相进攻，守擂成功即可获得丰厚的奖品。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160923/202450Nb-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 29px; width: 553px; height: 368px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	获奖者</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;比赛主办方iDareX敢玩表示，早在2015年，他们就举办了第一次北京SUP桨板公开赛，当时是第一次在北京举办此类比赛，比赛当天还有小雨，但参与者热情丝毫不减。今年是第二次举办，从一开始筹备就收到了圈内的重视。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;通过这次活动想让更多的运动爱好者接触桨板，也希望更多人了解桨板文化，从而爱上这项时尚健康的运动。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(205,36,'             ','北京市,极限运动,协会,登记,证书,点击,此处,','             ','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-161109150141G8.png\" style=\"width: 693px; height: 446px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/160728/1-160HR11635305.png\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 674px;\" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(206,37,'               ','分支机构','               ','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">北京市极限运动协会分支机构管理办法</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（2016年6月5日常务理事会议审议通过）</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第一章 总则</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为加强对北京市极限运动协会（以下简称本会）所属各分支机构的规范化管理，充分发挥协会整体功能，根据国务院《社会团体登记管理条例》、民政部《社会团体分支机构、代表机构登记办法》、及《北京市极限运动协会章程》等有关规定，特制定本办法。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第一条</strong> 本会各分支机构是根据自身发展需要，依据业务范围或会员组成的特点而设立的专门从事本会某项业务活动的机构，是本会的组成部分，接受本会理事会（常务理事会）的领导，不具有法人资格，其法律责任由本会承担。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第二条</strong> 分支机构可以称分会、运动项目委员会等。本办法适用于各分会、运动项目委员会。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第三条</strong> 分支机构的主要任务是：开展所属极限运动项目的普及以及推广、政策宣传、专业研究、技术培训、竞技竞赛、对外交流、咨询服务、承办委托；编辑出版极限运动专业刊物；充分发挥社会团体连接政府与市场的纽带作用，积极反映极限运动从业人员的意见与建议，服务广大会员，维护极限运动从业人员的合法权益；完成本会交办的各项任务。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第二章 分支机构的成立、挂靠、名称</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第四条</strong> 成立分支机构应具备下列条件：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）有规范的名称；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）有固定的住所，热心支持本会工作、具有法人资格的挂靠单位；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（三）有符合章程所规定的业务范围，并能开展相应的业务活动；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（四）有行业带头人和一定规模的专家群体；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（五）有合法和相对稳定的经费来源。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第五条</strong> 申请成立分支机构应由发起人和发起单位向本会提出书面申请，经本会常务理事会审查批准方可开展活动。筹备期间不得开展筹备以外的活动。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第六条</strong> 有下列情形之一的，协会不予受理：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）与本会已设立的分支机构业务范围、名称相同或相似的；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）在分支机构下又设立分支机构或代表机构的；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（三）拟设立的分支机构业务与本会宗旨、业务范围无关的；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（四）拟设立的分支机构设定的活动范围超越本会活动范围的；&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（五）有法律、法规禁止的其他情形的。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第七</strong>条 分支机构原则上挂靠具有极限运动专业优势的培训、经营等单位，挂靠单位应积极支持委员会工作，提供必要的办公条件，配备至少一名固定人员负责处理分支机构的日常工作。分支机构的挂靠与调整由本会秘书处提出建议，常务理事会决定。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第八条</strong> 本会各分支机构统称为：北京市极限运动协会&times;&times;分会或北京市极限运动协会&times;&times;委员会。不得在分支机构名称前直接冠以&ldquo;中国&rdquo;、&ldquo;中华&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国&rdquo;等字样，禁止使用&ldquo;北京市&times;&times;委员会&rdquo;、&ldquo;北京市&times;&times;分会&rdquo;或&ldquo;&times;&times;委员会&rdquo;、&ldquo;&times;&times;分会&rdquo;等不规范、不合法的称谓。分支机构开展各种活 动，均必须使用全称。分支机构的英文译名必须与中文名称一致。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第三章 分支机构委员会（理事会）及主要负责人</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第九条</strong> 分支机构实行委员会（理事会）制，每届任期三至五年。委员会委员（理事会理事）数量，不得超过其会员（含团体会员，下同）总数的1/3。因工作需要可设常务委员会（常务理事会），常委（常务理事）人数不得超过委员（理事）人数的1/3。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十条</strong> 分支机构设主任委员（理事长）一名、副主任委员(副理事长）若干名，人数不超过常委（常务理事）的1/5，秘书长一名。主任委员（理事长）任职年龄一般不 超过70周岁，秘书长任职年龄原则上不超过60岁，可连选连任，连任不超过两届。因特殊情况确需超过两届的，必须向本会说明理由，报本会审批。一人不得同 时兼任两个分支机构的主任委员或秘书长。党政机关副处以上干部兼任分支机构负责人的，应按干部管理权限报批。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十一条</strong> 分支机构须按期换届。每届任期届满前至少3个月，向本会提交书面改选换届申请报告，同时提交下届主任委员（理事长）、副主任委员（副理事长）、秘书长候选人建议名单，经本会审批同意后方可进行换届改选。到期不能按期换届的，须提交书面报告，说明原因。延期换届时间最长不超过1年。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第四章 &nbsp;变更与注销</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十二条</strong> 分支机构的变更应当向本会提交下列文件：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）分支机构主任委员（理事长）签署的变更申请书；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）分支机构委员会（理事会）或常委会（常务理事会）关于变更事项的会议决议；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（三）负责人变更需提交负责人继任人选的基本情况及身份证明；住所变更需提交新住所产权或使用证明。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十三条</strong> 分支机构注销提供下列文件：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）注销登记申请书；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）分支机构委员会（理事会）或常委会（常务理事会）关于注销的决议。本会根据分支机构的申请，报北京市民政局批准注销后，发给注销证明文件。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第五章 &nbsp; &nbsp;监督管理</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十四条&nbsp;</strong>分支机构应加强制度建设，不断推进民主、科学和制度化管理：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）分支机构必须接受本会领导，认真执行本会的决议，遵守本会各项规章制度，积极参加和支持本会各项活动；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）应建立符合《北京市极限运动协会章程》及有关规章制度的工作制度或管理办法，但不得制定分支机构章程；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（三）分支机构举办重大活动实行事前书面报告制度；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（四）分支机构应在每年十二月中旬向本会提交当年年度工作总结及下一年度工作计划；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十五条</strong> 分支机构在本会的授权范围内发展会员、代收会费。分支机构代为发展的会员属于本会会员，由本会统一发给会员证书，所收会费按15%上缴本会。未经授权不得发展会员和收缴会费。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十六条</strong> 分支机构除接受本会领导外，还应接受北京市社会团体登记管理机关的监督和检查。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十七条</strong> 分支机构不得再设立分支机构或代表机构。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十八条</strong> 本会按规定每年对分支机构进行年审，不定期对分支机构进行考核评估（考核评估办法另行制订），年审或考核评估中如发现分支机构存在以下问题的，将视不同情况给予责令改正、限期停止活动、更换分支机构主要负责人、调整挂靠单位、注销分支机构等处罚：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（一）一年内无任何活动，无法正常开展学会活动；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（二）无固定办公场所；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（三）无故不参加年检；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（四）在年检中弄虚作假；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（五）擅自开立银行基本账户；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">（六）违反会员发展和会费收缴及上缴等有关规定。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第六章 附则</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第十九条&nbsp;</strong>本办法于2016年6月5日经本会常务理事会审议通过，自下发之日起施行。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>第二十条</strong> 本办法解释权归本会秘书处。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>北京市极限运动协会</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>2016年6月6日</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(207,38,'          ','二维码,公共微信平台','          ','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会官方微信公关平台已开始运营，关注北京市极限运动协会的极限运动运动员、爱好者，可微信扫描以下二维码，即刻关注，获得北京市极限运动协会新鲜内容推送：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161019/1-161019102Z0E6.jpg\" style=\"width: 258px; height: 258px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(208,39,'       ','北京市,极限运动,协会,会费,管理办法,按照,','       ','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 按照《北京市极限运动协会章程》第十一条《会员履行下列义务》第四款和《北京市极限运动协会财务管理制度》第二款之规定，制定协会会费管理办法如下：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">一、协会会员要按时交纳会费。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">二、会费标准</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">1．个人会员50元/年；首次70元/年（50+20元工本费）；弱势群体和贫困个人视情况可减免；</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2．团体会员500元/年。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">三、会费由分部和团体会员负责人收缴。每年第一季度上交总部。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">四、会员会费为协会组织开展活动的合法收入，现金或支票必须按照财务管理条例及时入协会账户，不准另立帐户或挪用。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">五、按照《北京市极限运动协会章程》第十二条之规定， 会员一年不交纳会费或不参加本团体活动，视为自动退会。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">北京市极限运动协会</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2016年6月</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(209,40,'         ','北京,极限运动,协会,安全,责任,制度,安全,','         ','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 安全工作是整个工作的保障，为加强北京市极限运动协会（以下简称本会）安全工作的管理，确保本会日常安全，落实安全经营管理目标责任制，根据有关规定，结合本会实际，制定本制度。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、贯彻落实法规。要依法管理好联盟的安全工作，认真贯彻落实《安全生产法》、《消防法》、《机关、团体、企事业单位消防安全管理规定》、《北京市安全生产条例》，建立本会的安全责任制和安全责任追究制。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、安全组织制度。建立健全本会的安全管理组织，本会要建立法人代表负总责的安全工作领导小组；结合本会实际设立安全机构或分管机构；配备专职安全管理人员，达到日常工作有领导有分工，具体工作有人管。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、安全责任制度。本会法人代表是本会安全工作的第一责任人，按照&ldquo;一岗双则&rdquo;的要求，加强对安全工作的领导，落实好安全经营管理目标责任制，结合本会际，分解工作指标，层层落实到每个负责人、员工和经营场所，并签订安全责任书，明确安全权利、义务和责任。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 四、健全安全管理制度。结合本会实际，建立健全本会内部的便于考核，易于操作，责任明确的安全工作管理制度，使安全管理工作制度化、规范化。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 五、安全会议制度。本会每季度召开一次安全工作会议，贯彻落实有关安全工作的会议、文件精神和相关法规政策，分析本会的安全状况，部署安全工作任务，并做好规范的会议记录。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 六、加强安全检查制度。本会每季度至少组织一次全面安全检查，按照&ldquo;谁检查谁负责&rdquo;的要求，做好检查记录，由检查人员在检查记录上签字并存档。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 七、安全隐患整改制度。对发现的安全隐患要立即整改，按照&ldquo;谁整改谁负责&rdquo;的要求，由整改人员在整改记录上签字并存档。对暂时不能整改的，除落实责任人，加强防范措施外，要落实整改资金投入计划，限期进行整改。按照市安委会等部门的统一部署，落实好安全治理工作任务。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 八、安全教育培训制度。本会要制定安全教育培训计划，培训计划要形成书面材料，做好培训记录。相关负责人、管理人员，要积极参加安监等部门组织的安全管理资格证书的培训和考核；&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 九、 安全生产经营档案管理制度。本会要建立健全安全档案管理制度，以备查本会的安全管理情况。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 十、事故上报制度。一旦发生事故，要立即报告相关主管部门。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 十一、安全工作奖惩制度。本会要把安全工作列入本会的考核机制，对安全工作进行奖惩。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 十二、安全保险制度。本会要按照有关规定，足额缴纳工伤保险，确保员工的合法权益。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 十三、落实好安委会、安监、消防等部门部署的各项工作任务。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 十四、本制度经2016年年6 月5日北京市极限运动协会第一届会员大会表决通过，自通过之日起生效。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">北京市极限运动协会</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2016年6月5日</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(210,41,'             ','全国,职业,跑酷,健身,教练,资格认证,课程,','             ','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">课程背景</span></strong></strong></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2014年，在国务院将全民健身上升为国家战略的大的时代背景下，越来越多的人们加入到了全民健身的队伍中来。从健身意识的觉醒到健身观念趋向成熟，人们对运动项目的要求也越来也高。体育消费逐渐向项目专业化、受众精准化方向发展。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会作为运动类行业协会，致力于极限运动的普及推广、专业研究和技术培训。为了给行业、国家储备更多的专业跑酷教练人才，继而为更多普通人群能够更好的了解、接触到跑酷这项极限运动。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为此，北京市极限运动协会，联合&ldquo;自由印迹&rdquo;运动培训学院，打造《专业跑酷健身教练职业资格认证》课程体系。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<fieldset style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25px; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 5px 5px 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\">\r\n	<legend style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.8em; text-align: center;\"></legend>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px;\">招生简章</span></strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">招生对象</span></strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">1.追求私教课程更具特色、更加丰富的私人教练精英。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">2. 希望通过跑酷让自己成为健身房焦点的教练精英。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">3.有志于投身跑酷教学，却苦于没有理论基础和教学体系的跑酷练习者。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">4.已经开始跑酷教学，却面临&ldquo;教学瓶颈期&rdquo;的跑酷教练员。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">5.准备步入大健康产业的其它项目运动人士。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">6.须年满18周岁。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 39px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 16.1px;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</fieldset>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">课程设置</span></strong></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">开课日期</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2016年12月1日-7日</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">1. 集中培训期</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">7天（50课时）</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">性质：集中培训</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2. 技术积累期</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">6天（性质：预约技术实战）</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;跑酷的理念可以短期掌握，但跑酷的技术须有积累期。所以，在集中培训结束后，学员可以以预约的形式自由安排6天的技术积累课程，场馆有跑酷实践教练帮助大家熟悉跑酷技术。考虑到教练职业的忙碌，自由预约的方式可以让大家更合理的安排自己的工作时间。具体信息请开课后咨询个人的课程顾问。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">课程内容</span></strong></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>1. 跑 酷</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷的起源</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷的文化</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷的概念</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷的实际作用</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2. 基础运动理论知识培训</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.什么是教练？</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.教练的职业操守</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.教练所扮演的角色</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.运动生理学</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.运动营养学</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷体适能基础理论</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷运动功能解剖学</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.身体关联理论</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">3. 跑酷运动体态评估体系</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">作为教练，在给学员开始教学之前，我们的首要任务是要了解学员的身体情况，因为只有充分了解学员的情况，我们才能更安全、更有针对性的提高学员的训练水平。否则，一味的盲目加量，可能会导致身体出现不可逆的损伤。 而&ldquo;跑酷体态评估体系&rdquo;则是为安全防护在源头建起了一道防火墙。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">4. 18个跑酷基础动作的讲解</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.各个跑酷动作对身体的益处</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.动作的起始、完成位置</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷动作的分解以及产生流程</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.动作过程中的注意事项：</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">呼吸、手法、幅度、类型、参与部位、FITT</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.各个动作容易犯的错误</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.穿越类、反弹类、跳跃类、摆荡类、悬挂类、爬行类、翻腾类七大技术动作体系的关键点讲解</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.实用性：动作适合地形</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.动作中为学员保护时的站位</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">5. 课程编排</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.如何制定一个高粘着度的跑酷训练计划</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.如何将跑酷融入到私教课程</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.一节特色跑酷私教课的操作流程</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷精品小班课程的编排</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷团体大课的编排</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">6. 跑酷教学表格体系的意义及使用方式</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《健康问答表》 &nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《测试表格》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《体位评估表》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《计划编排表》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《饮食建议表》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《上课记录表》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.《总结评估表格》</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">7. 运动损伤</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷运动前的损伤预防</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷运动中的风险规避</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.跑酷运动损伤后的处理</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">8. 普拉提在跑酷课程中的运用</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">9. 销售</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.如何自我管理</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.销售者应具备的素质</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.沟通技巧</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.客户人格分析以及应对策略</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.销售理念以及经验分享</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">10. 教学的实战模拟</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">11. 考核</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.考试合格者予以北京市极限运动协会《跑酷职业证书》。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">.考试初次不通过学员，可申请三次旁听及补考。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">课程内容</span></strong></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">1.体育局领导将深度解读当前政策和阐述社会体育未来的发展方向。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">2.本次认证课程为国内首次针对当前国情开发的跑酷健身教学体系。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">3.协会将为参加培训认证的学员提供为期一年的免费技术支持。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">4. 北京市极限运动协会与大家携手共同搭建一个大的平台，为未来行业发展、职业极限运动教练员个人事业发展奠基，同舟共济，共建共享。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\'; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.8px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 8, 48); text-shadow: rgb(201, 201, 201) 5px 3px 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">导师团队</span></strong></strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">导师：王伟</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>资历</strong>：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会会长；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">自由印迹体育总经理；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">自由印迹运动培训学院培训导师。</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">体育行业从业十年以上，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">历练于倍力、韦德体系，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">师从健美国家队总教练杨敬民老师。</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">宾至中国会所项目负责人、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京裘马都会所运营经理、</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京道生堂太极常务副总经理、</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京红玺台会所总经理、</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">在体育专业培训、体育场馆的运营体系建立、营销模式的建立以及会所管理方面积累了丰富的经验。&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">导师：吴优良</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>资历</strong>：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会副会长；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京一兆韦德健身教学部主管；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">自由印迹运动培训学院培训导师；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">美国PMA普拉提床高级教练；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">亚洲运动及体适能高级教练；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">亚洲健康运动管理学院产前产后私人教练认证；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市健身健美高级私人教练；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京王严健身健美高级技术教练；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">拥有十年以上健身从业及教学经验，累计接近20000小时私教课教学经验；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">曾为多位明星进行运动指导；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">经多年积累总结出一套对于健身和极限运动的训练理念和技术体系。</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">导师：杜林森</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">资历：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会监事；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">森健身公司总经理；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">自由印迹运动培训学院培训导师；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">退役于西部某特种攻坚英雄连 &nbsp;；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">一线影视明星御用私人教练；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">国际体适能学院高级私人教练证书；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">飞萨弗Network普拉提专业教练认证；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">4S脊椎康复暨四肢关节康复认证；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">海莱特康复手法认证；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">苗振诺亚第拉伸疗法；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">博士博莱肌筋膜琏；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">李欣普拉提。</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">国内大部分的主流培训课程，结合自己十年无间断在职工作，累计18000余小时私教教学经验，总结形成自己对运动教学的训练体系，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">曾帮助千余名会员达到自己的健身目的。</span></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">导师：张磊</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">资历：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会副会长；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会跑酷委员会会长；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中国跑酷领跑人；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">极限梦跑酷俱乐部创始人；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">自由印迹运动培训学院培训导师；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">2015年获得跑酷体能培训师称号；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">轻体能跑酷训练研发领头人；</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px