	(211,42,'                              ','授牌,协会,极限运动,极限运动协会,健身工作室','                              ','<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;11月6日上午，北京市极限运动协会迎来了又一个新成员。北京攻坚体育文化发展有限公司旗下UPLIFT健身工作室正式成为北京市极限运动协会会员单位。</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京市极限运动协会秘书长刘垒占先生，副会长张磊先生以及北京攻坚体育文化传播有限公司总经理杜林森先生等相关负责人出席授牌仪式。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-16110914263MD.jpg\" style=\"width: 553px; height: 369px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;作为北京市极限运动协会的综合体能训练基地之一，同时也开展行业人才的培养，以及大众极限健身体系的研发。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在签约授牌仪式上，北京攻坚体育文化传播有限公司负责人杜林森先生表示愿意与协会共同成长，为社会体育的发展做出自己的贡献。北京市极限运动协会秘书长刘垒占先生也表示，协会作为一个面向社会的非营利机构，将会努力做大做强，为会员带来更多的增值服务。授牌仪式氛围和谐融洽。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-161109142G54K.jpg\" style=\"width: 553px; height: 369px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">(左起：协会秘书长刘垒占，北京攻坚体育负责人杜林森，协会副会长张磊)</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-161109142K1326.jpg\" style=\"width: 553px; height: 369px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会作为运动类行业协会，致力于极限运动的普及推广、专业研究和技术培训。在全民健身上升为国家战略的新的时代背景下，协会愿意与各界同仁携手，为中国从体育大国到体育强国的转变贡献自己的力量。</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-161109143352446.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 335px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161109/1-161109143414F4.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 450px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Uplift健身工作室</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(212,43,'            ','活动,比赛,光猪跑','            ','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二届光猪爬山节由北京市极限运动协会理事崔建民先生（纸箱哥）发起，北京车库主办、北京市极限运动协会协办，于2016年11月12日在房山周口店金祖山景区举行，参与人数达到了一百余人。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G35FL16.jpg\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G35J2311.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 427px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;上午十点半活动正式开始，纸箱哥带上自己的纸箱由景区入口出发，和众多参与者一同开启本次光猪爬活动。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G40014914.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 427px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G4002M61.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 878px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第二届房山光猪节彩绘图集</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G40115443.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 878px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">第二届房山光猪节彩绘图集</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">光猪节的起源</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;源于美国的滑雪胜地&mdash;科罗拉多州克雷斯特德比特山的滑雪场，每逢严冬将逝之际，男男女女的滑雪能手将衣服脱得一件不留，毫无遮掩地在雪中穿行。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这个传统让前卫人士趋之若鹜，在蓝天白云下脱光衣服滑雪是亲近自然的超级享受，许多恋人更会借此机会坦诚相对。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G4024Y46.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 284px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G4025MO.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 466px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">国内各类光猪节越来越多</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2012年2月26日，首届北京&ldquo;光猪跑&rdquo;比赛在奥林匹克森林公园举行。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;几十名跑步爱好者汇聚奥林匹克森林公园，展开一场别开生面的&ldquo;裸奔&rdquo;活动。此次活动由网友自发组织，被称为&ldquo;光猪跑&rdquo;。参赛者须穿着内衣裤裸跑3.5公里以完成比赛，组织者希望以此方式提倡人们亲近自然、健康生活。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G40355O1.jpg\" style=\"width: 640px; height: 392px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161127/1-16112G40404307.jpg\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 376px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(213,44,'        ','跑酷,跑酷资格认证,跑酷教练','        ','<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2016</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">12</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">3</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">日，由国家体育总局领导监审，北京市极限运动协会联合</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">自由印迹运动培训学院</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">开展的为期</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">7</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">天的全国首届</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\"> </span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">《专业跑酷体能教练》资格认证在</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">北京睿腾体能馆</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">顺利开课。来自全国各地，有志于从事跑酷大众教学的</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">20</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">多位学员参与本次培训及考核认证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151UKL49.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151UQT62.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 北京市极限运动协会作为体育类行业协会，致力于极限运动的普及推广、专业研究和技术培训。协会以本次培训认证为起点，并逐步开展的《体能教练资格认证课程》将给行业、国家、储备更多的专业人才。同时极限运动的大众化教学也会让更多的老百姓能够从中受益！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151USD02.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:11px;\">国家体育总局领导现场解读政策，抓住社会体育的历史新机遇</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151U94A96.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">本次培训以</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">科学规范、实用至上</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&rdquo;</span></strong><span style=\"font-kerning: none\"><strong>为宗旨进行课程的编排。课程体系完善，环环相扣，知识覆盖面广，流程操作性强。课程内容如下：</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">跑酷运动起源的讲解</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">社会体育市场的展望，以及如何把握当前历史机遇</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">运动生理学、运动解剖学、力学原理、运动营养学等人体科学的培训</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">跑酷体能训练人群体态评估的培训</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">课程的编排以及操作流程</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">运动损伤的预防以及损伤后的处理</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">跑酷运动</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">18</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">个基础动作的详细讲解及运用</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">l&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">教学的实战模拟</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151Z011417.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 401px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151Z022138.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 本次培训师资力量雄厚，</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Tahoma; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\"> </span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">导师均从事运动行业十年以上，在拥有完善知识体系的同时，也具备了超强的实战经验！能够最大程度的帮助学员更快、更扎实的掌握课程内容，并且将所学灵活的运用于跑酷教学当中。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151Z03GY.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/161215/1-1612151Z04aU.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在国务院将全民健身上升为国家战略的大的时代背景下，越来越多的人们加入到了全民健身的队伍中来。从健身意识的觉醒到健身观念趋向成熟，人们对运动项目的要求也越来也高。体育消费逐渐向项目专业化、受众精准化方向发展。北京市极限运动协会欢迎更多喜爱极限运动的朋友的加入，让我们在共同感受极限运动魅力的同时，为中国从体育大国向体育强国的转变贡献我们的力量。</span></p>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(214,45,'                 ','北京市,极限运动,协会,与,睿腾,体能,馆,授牌,','                 ','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12月28日，北京市极限运动协会迎来了又一个重量级成员，北京睿腾体能馆正式成为北京市极限运动协会会员单位。同时，作为北京市极限运动协会&ldquo;跑酷体能训练基地&rdquo;，睿腾体能馆与协会在《青少年体能训练课程》的研发以及《专业跑酷体能教练》的培养、输出上达成重要合作。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/170103/1-1F1031T153R2.jpg\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 524px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">左：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">秘书长刘垒占 &nbsp; &nbsp;右：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">睿腾体能馆创始人姚辉</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会秘书长刘垒占先生与睿腾体能馆创始人姚辉先生，以及其他负责人共同出席授牌仪式。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/170103/1-1F1031S920193.jpg\" style=\"width: 450px; height: 629px;\" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;睿腾体育成立于2011年，主要提供家庭式运动训练服务，致力于提升学员及整个家庭成员的身体机能和运动能力，并从中收获自信与健康。睿腾体育先后在望京、顺义等7个场馆及国际学校开设运动培训课程，有上千名小学员。通过多年的积累和总结，睿腾体育在青少年体能训练领域颇有建树。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/170103/1-1F1031S932X5.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 370px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;体能馆地处文化氛围浓厚的马泉营艺术区，环境优雅舒适，设施专业齐全，非常适合跑酷培训以及个人综合体能训练、企业团建等活动的开展。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/170103/1-1F1031R95c95.png\" style=\"width: 627px; height: 471px;\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在签约授牌仪式上，睿腾体能馆姚辉先生表示愿意与协会共同成长，为社会体育的发展做出自己的贡献。北京市极限运动协会秘书长刘垒占先生也表示：&ldquo;协会作为一个面向社会的非营利机构，将会努力做大做强，为会员带来更多的增值服务。授牌仪式氛围和谐融洽。&rdquo;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/170103/1-1F1031S94D33.png\" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;北京市极限运动协会作为运动类行业协会，致力于极限运动的普及推广、专业研究和技术培训。在全民健身上升为国家战略的新的时代背景下，协会愿意与各界同仁携手，为中国从体育大国到体育强国的转变贡献自己的力量。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
