	(236,67,'      ','正式,成为,北京市,体育,总会,会员单位,2017,年,','    ','<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">2017</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">年</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">月</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">25</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">日，北京市体育总会为北京极限运动协会颁发会员证书，今日起，北京市极限运动协会正式成为北京市体育总会会员单位。</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191359_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191359_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 北京市</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">体育总会</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">，</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">原名中华全国体育总会北京分会，成立于</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">1950</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">年，是北京市群众性的</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">体育</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">团体。</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none; color: #3e3e3e\">宗旨为</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">：协同北京市体育局，团结全市体育工作者，发展北京市体育事业，增强人民</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none; color: #3e3e3e\">体质</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">，提高运动技术水平，增进北京市与各国人民之间的友谊。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191415_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"369\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191415_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </b>北京市体育总会的主要任务是：开展群众性体育竞赛及表演活动，组织社会调查，反映群众对体育工作的意见，通过各体育协会举办体育业务学习，开展体育宣传，向体育爱好者、工作者进行</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">爱国</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">主义、国际主义、体育方针政策和体育道德教育，</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">促进</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">国际体育</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">交流</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">活动。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191431_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"400\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191431_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191459_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"299\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191459_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191530_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"341\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170330/1_170330191530_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 未来，北京市极限运动协会</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none; color: #3e3e3e\">将</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">在北京市体育总会的指导与引领下，积极响应国家号召，为推广极限运动及全民健身奉献力量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-09-02 13:47:39'),
