rosoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">男子街式</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">女子<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">街式</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">男子碗池</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">女子<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">碗池</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">三、运动员资格</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、年龄在16岁至40岁（1977年1月1日至2001年12月31日间出生）的中华人民共和国公民；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">以下条件至少满足一项：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">1）户籍（以二代身份证住址为准）所在地为北京。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">2）具有北京高校正式学籍（在教育部高校学生司注册备案）的普通全日制在校6个月以上的学生。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">3）入伍部队所在地为北京的运动员。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: Helvetica; text-indent: 7px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">四、竞赛办法</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">1、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">执行中国轮滑协会制定的《2017滑板竞赛规则（暂停）》；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">2、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">方式：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px; font-size: 12px;\">1）男、女街式分别进行两轮比赛。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px; font-size: 12px;\">2）男、女碗池分别进行四轮比赛。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px; font-size: 12px;\">3）以每轮比赛得分的高分轮分数作为最终得分，并据此排定名次。如两人（或两人以上）高分轮得分相同，则根据低分轮的得分排定名次。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\">五、联系方式</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 7px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">电话1：132 4143 9567 刘老师</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 7px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">电话2：186 1109 0051 王老师&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 7px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">邮箱：bjesa_freedom@163.com</span></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(239,70,'      ','体育大会，北京市体育大会，极限单车，跑酷','      ','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181701_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181701_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8px;\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Songti SC\'; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">从左至右：北京市体育局群众体育处处长史江平、人民网副总裁唐维红、北京市体育局副局长杨海滨、人民网体育部主任朱凯</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Songti SC\'; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5月4日，第九届北京市体育大会新闻发布暨启动仪式在人民网演播大厅召开，人民网副总裁唐维红，北京市体育局副局长、北京市体育总会副主席杨海滨出席活动，市体育局相关部门领导、各承办协会及在京主要媒体记者参加，启动仪式上发布了第九届北京市体育大会相关信息，并进行了风筝、毽绳、航空模型、回春保健操、空竹、极限运动等项目的表演展示，正式拉开了体育大会的序幕。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181729_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181729_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Songti SC\'; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 北京市体育大会是由北京市体育局和北京市体育总会主办，北京市级体育协会承办的综合性群众健身体育竞赛活动，旨在进一步宣传贯彻《北京市全民健身条例》，贯彻落实《北京市全民健身实施计划（2016-2020年）》，推动全民健身和全民健康深度融合，满足人民群众日益增长的健身需求，促进北京市群众体育工作的发展，加强体育组织和基层健身团队体系建设，为体育社团开展全民健身活动搭建平台，普及推广冰雪运动，推进京津冀协调发展，落实全民健身国家战略，为实现从体育大国向体育强国迈进的目标添砖加瓦。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181825_1.jpg\" width=\"550\" border=\"0\" height=\"366\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505181825_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 15, 15); font-family: \'Songti SC\'; font-size: 12px;\">北京市体育总会秘书长王品熙公布第九届北京市体育大会竞赛规程</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(123, 123, 111);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(123, 123, 111);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 自2009年创办以来，北京市体育大会已成功举办八届，以群众喜闻乐见的赛事活动为基础，项目设置不断扩充、丰富，由最初的25个项目扩大到45个，累积参与健身爱好者达百万人次，34个市级体育社团依托体育大会的举办，扩大了会员数量，丰富了活动建设，提高了协会综合实力。</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182234_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182234_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Songti SC\'; font-size: 12px;\">人民网副总裁唐维红致辞</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: \'Songti SC\'; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为增强体育大会的广泛参与性，提高体育大会的社会影响力，为市民、体育爱好者提供安全、科学和丰富的全民健身平台，本届体育大会设指定项目和邀请项目，赛事活动面向社会、面向社区、面向市民，也包括协会团体会员、个人会员，分多场次多地点多阶段举行，每个项目参赛人员800人以上。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182919_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182919_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Songti SC\'; font-size: 12px;\">论坛现场</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 届时，篮球、足球、体育舞蹈、龙舟、风筝、空竹、跑酷等40余个项目的比赛活动将陆续展开。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 市体育局、市体育总会印制了统一的获奖证书，为取得优异成绩的选手进行颁发，增添体育大会参与者的荣誉感和自豪感，为社会各阶层、各年龄段参与体育健身搭建更大的平台。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 其中不乏一些高水平体育爱好者，充分发挥体育社团在本领域内先进引领作用，迎来一场体育爱好者全民健身活动的盛会，整个体育大会期间将吸引数万名体育爱好者参与。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182959_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"275\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505182959_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">北京市极限运动协会会长王伟现场发言</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 北京市极限运动协会会长王伟在现场对如何正确认识极限运动</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\';\">以及如何让更多的老百姓通过极限运动受益</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\';\">进行了发言阐述。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">部分协会项目展演</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: left; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183050_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183050_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">极限单车</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183150_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"800\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183150_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\">跑酷 、极限单车</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183233_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183233_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">滑板</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183323_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183323_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">少儿跑酷&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183355_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183355_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">少儿跑酷：王浩宇、李艾米尔，跑酷：张磊、崔健，极限单车：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">赵雪峰、王鹏，滑板：张啸萌</span></p>\r\n<p 