\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183711_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">毽球表演</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183733_1.jpg\" width=\"500\" border=\"0\" height=\"333\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170505/1_170505183733_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">空竹表演</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 本届体育大会报名工作由各承办协会独立完成，凡欲参与体育大会比赛的爱好者可登陆北京市体育总会网站查看各项目竞赛信息及报名方式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://sports.people.com.cn/GB/31928/412339/index.html\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><strong>点击此处查看北京市体育大会启动仪式&nbsp;</strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(240,71,'      ','大型,户外运动,综艺节目,“,街头之王,”,','      ','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">经过近一年的筹备，大型户外街头运动综艺节目</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">街头之王</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">于本月底在北京国际饭店正式举办新闻发布暨启动仪式。</span> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 该节目将以海选、半决赛、决赛、全国总决赛的层层选拔，最后选出最顶尖的街头极限运动高手，也为了让更多人了解并参与到街头极限运动中来。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170608/1_170608202732_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170608/1_170608202732_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 北京市极限运动协会会长王伟表示：极限运动进入中国是上世纪</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">90</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">年代，以挑战身体极限，超越自我为特征，受到了年轻一代的狂热追捧。随着国家物质文化的发展，随着一代又一代极限人的努力，极限运动在国内生长的土壤越来越肥沃。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 尽管如此，至今仍有不少人对这项运动存在误解，认为它是纯粹追求冒险的运动。其实极限运动不像大家想象的那么危险，极限挑战只是极限运动的一个分支，而不是全部。极限运动的训练呈循序渐进的体系，挑战有专业配备和保障。极限运动在让大家享受超越自我乐趣的同时，也具有极大的健身功效。</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">街头之王</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">这个节目的启动，有利于更好地推广这项运动，进而达到全民参与的目的。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 极限运动是一些难度较高、挑战性较大的运动项目的统称，如滑板、跑酷、极限轮滑、极限单车、攀岩、雪板、冲浪、街道疾降、极限越野、极限滑水等都属于极限运动项目。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 因此，街头之王这档综艺节目将是目前国内所有综艺节目中，类型极其特殊的、表现形式难度较高，并且具有极高专业水准的一档极限运动节目。主办方欢迎更多极限运动的职业选手、专业动作影星、极限运动爱好者共同参与。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); min-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 该节目已正式启动报名。选手可就近选择北京、昆明、成都、沈阳、乌鲁木齐、深圳、哈尔滨、太原、郑州、上海、合肥、南京、呼和浩特等</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">13</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">个国内赛区，美国纽约、韩国首尔</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">2</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">个国外赛区进行报名，然后经过两个月的层层选拔，最终各赛区优胜者会师北京进行全国总决赛。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Songti SC\'; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</p>','2017-08-18 19:01:05','2017-08-18 19:01:05'),
	(241,72,'            ','全运会,北京,滑板,队,选拔,结果,公布,十名,','            ','<p><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">全国运动会（中华人民共和国全国运动会）简称</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">全运会</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">是中国国内水平最高，规模最大的综合性运动会。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 全运会的比赛项目除武术外基本与奥运会相同，其原意是为国家的奥运战略锻炼新人、选拔人才。全运会每四年举办一次，一般在奥运会年前后举行。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 今年，第十三届全运会将于8月在天津举行，滑板作为首次进入奥运会、全运会的项目，又因为其在全国范围内备受年轻人的喜爱，是具有超高的人气的运动项目，继而得到更多关注。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170608/1_170608204255_1.jpg\" width=\"640\" border=\"0\" height=\"396\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170608/1_170608204255_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 上月，由 <b>北京市体育局</b>、<b>北京市体育总会 </b>主办，<b>北京市极限运动协会 </b>承办的北京滑板队选拔赛在京顺利举行。赛中，每位参赛选手都展现出自身的精湛实力，过程精彩异常，最终选拔出十名优秀的滑板选手，代表北京参加</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">6</span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">月在江苏南京进行的全运会滑板项目预选赛。名单如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; min-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; min-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC Semibold\';\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\"><b>参赛队员</b>：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\"><b>女子</b>：陈沛雯</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\"> </span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">杨浠镮</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\"><b>男子</b>：李垌</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\'; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">李文金</span><span style