	(243,74,'北京滑板队在此次全国滑板锦标赛中，共取得一金三银的好成绩。','全国,滑板,锦标赛,暨,全运会,项目,预选赛,2017,','北京滑板队在此次全国滑板锦标赛中，共取得一金三银的好成绩。','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2017</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">年全国滑板锦标赛暨全运会滑板项目预选赛，于</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">6</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">9</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">日至</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; -webkit-font-kerning: none;\">11</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-kerning: none;\">日在南京市龙江体育馆、南京鱼嘴体育公园举行。</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-kerning: none\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 此次比赛由国家体育总局社会体育指导中心、中国轮滑协会、江苏省体育局主办，江苏省社会体育管理中心、江苏省轮滑协会、南京市体育局承办，南京市龙江体育运动学校、南京市滨江公园管理处协办。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/allimg/170626/1_170626191024_1.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" style=\"cursor:pointer\" onclick=\"window.open(\'/uploads/allimg/170626/1_170626191024_1.jpg\')\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\'; min-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-hyphens: auto; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;